data.description: Welcome to Tanglewood! This spacious 5 bedroom 3 bath home is waiting for you. Situated on a spacious 1 acre lot, this property offers plenty of room for outdoor activities and relaxation. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by a charming barn door that add a touch of rustic elegance to the home's entrance. Waiting behind the barn door is the perfect area to create your private getaway! The main floor boasts a spacious guest room along with a full bathroom just down the hall. The open concept kitchen allows for you to be part of the fun. Upstairs you will find three generously sized bedrooms that share a fully remodeled bathroom as well as the oversized master bedroom and walk in closet. Don't miss the oversized 2 car garage that has an extra area for storage as well. Located in a peaceful neighborhood, this property offers a tranquil retreat and allows you to enjoy the privacy and serenity while being only minutes away from town. Call 678-386-7711 today for your private tour!
